channel.title: Witch [377] server should i start with?
channel.description:
[b]M[/b][b]E[/b][b]T[/b][b]A[/b][b]L[/b] here,
I have a question that might me easy for some people to answer. But first a little about me since this is my first post... I've been working on a server that hasn't been released to the public for a quite some time it's a 317 now. I started before Miss Silabsoft released her client with the newer items. So i've been working on it for some time now, i've put the newer items on including Dragon Plate body, Dragon Claws, ECT, ECT. But I want to convert all my work into a [377] server.. For the people that are gonna say "LOL noob you can't do that." Witch people will say that. I converted my work from an old server to a [317]. I admit some stuff didn't work but most of it did. So I will post another topic somewhere else saying my accomplishments on my server.
So if you have any suggestions on a starting [377] server please post here I'm been looking, i've got one i might use but I want to here from you guys/girls.
